"'''Turn Blue'''" is a song by American [[Rock music|rock]] band [[The Black Keys]], and the title track from their album ''[[Turn Blue (album)|Turn Blue]]''. It was co-written and co-produced by the band and [[Danger Mouse (musician)|Danger Mouse]].

The song was written in February 2013 while The Black Keys frontman [[Dan Auerbach]] and his wife Stephanie Gonis were in the midst of divorce proceedings. <ref>[http://www.songfacts.com/detail.php?id=33234 Turn Blue by The Black Keys] - ''SongFacts'' (accessed November 28, 2014)</ref>
